WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.429 --> 00:00:01.714
Good morning, everybody.

00:00:01.714 --> 00:00:06.667
I just wanted to come on and tell you all a word that the Lord has for you today.

00:00:06.667 --> 00:00:09.000
I just want to introduce my son, Braden.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:09.855
'Hey, what's up?

00:00:10.425 --> 00:00:14.073
I'm the editor for 90% of his videos.

00:00:14.073 --> 00:00:15.140
I edit the shorts.

00:00:15.140 --> 00:00:17.829
You guys are being nice to me in the comments; you're all asking, 'Who's the editor?

00:00:17.829 --> 00:00:19.000
' and it was me.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.680
' The Lord's really gifted him, and he's trying really hard.

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:23.635
'Yeah, I try to make them match.

00:00:23.635 --> 00:00:25.613
I try to do the math and stuff.

00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:28.644
It's a lot of work, but I hope you all enjoy it; it's fun.

00:00:28.644 --> 00:00:29.963
' He's 15 years old.

00:00:29.963 --> 00:00:34.344
'Yeah, I try to make the shorts, try to pick the topics and stuff.

00:00:34.344 --> 00:00:45.000
So if you guys have any ideas for shorts, just let me know down in the comments so I can make some better shorts because everybody seems to really like the end-time stuff—what's going to happen and what we're fixing to head into.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:50.213
' This is my son right here; I'm really proud of him.

00:00:50.213 --> 00:00:56.707
He works really hard, he's really smart, he does well at school, and he loves Jesus with all his heart.

00:00:56.707 --> 00:00:58.642
'Yeah, I try really hard.

00:01:03.755 --> 00:01:03.971
I have a good upcoming short soon; I'm making it right now.

00:01:03.971 --> 00:01:05.446
' Oh, praise the Lord!

00:01:19.004 --> 00:01:19.260
I just wanted to bring him on here and show him off.

00:01:32.546 --> 00:01:32.751
I'm really proud of him and just tell people that he loves Jesus.

00:01:32.751 --> 00:01:39.457
I'm going to bring each one of my children on and introduce them to you all.

00:01:39.457 --> 00:01:45.720
This is the day I told him I wanted to introduce the man behind the camera.

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:51.733
He's my prayer; he prays with me.

00:02:01.911 --> 00:02:02.109
He sits with me every night and we intercede, and I'm teaching him how to intercede and dip in those rivers.

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:06.960
He's learned a lot.

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:07.714
We take communion.

00:02:11.399 --> 00:02:11.760
He was there whenever we raised the dog from the dead.

00:02:11.760 --> 00:02:16.380
He was there whenever I squashed the dog to death by accident.

00:02:22.070 --> 00:02:22.420
Yeah, it was by accident.

00:02:29.340 --> 00:02:29.580
My wife's behind the camera right now; she's holding the camera.

00:02:29.580 --> 00:02:39.110
If you haven't seen that video, we'll link it in the description.

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:46.110
God raised that dog from the dead; it was special.

00:02:46.110 --> 00:02:51.015
Ever since he was a little baby boy in diapers, I've been teaching him.

00:02:51.015 --> 00:02:57.579
He's been baptized in the Holy Ghost and speaking in tongues since he was five years old.

00:02:57.579 --> 00:03:05.983
He sees in the spirit too, and the Lord shows him things in dreams.

00:03:11.264 --> 00:03:12.439
It's the same with my daughter, and you'll meet her, probably in the next video—our youngest daughter.

00:03:12.439 --> 00:03:15.780
Family is important to me, and I just wanted to show you all my son and introduce you.

00:03:15.780 --> 00:03:17.219
He's a real blessing.

00:03:17.219 --> 00:03:20.700
Okay, about the spirit of forebodings and being in intercessory prayer.

00:03:20.700 --> 00:03:41.435
This is very important that you hear this because there are a lot of times you can feel that heaviness—you feel that urge to intercede and you're in the moment and you're like, 'Man, I feel like there's a weight in the spirit realm on you.

00:03:41.435 --> 00:03:51.179
' What happens is the demonic tries to imitate the spiritual realm, and the devil tries to push you into things—push, push, push.

00:03:51.179 --> 00:04:00.909
This is one of the instances of what I'm trying to tell you: you can walk around and always have a spirit of heaviness.

00:04:00.909 --> 00:04:03.090
It's like a heaviness on you.

00:04:05.865 --> 00:04:07.700
You think, 'Well, it's the Lord and the burden to pray.

00:04:07.700 --> 00:04:09.299
' No, it's not.

00:04:09.299 --> 00:04:18.439
There's a spirit of forebodings and it tries to come on and push you into that place to make you not live in a state of joy.

00:04:18.439 --> 00:04:22.830
The fruit of the Spirit is love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness, gentleness, and self-control.

00:04:25.395 --> 00:04:31.778
You need to understand that when you're not walking in that joy, when you're not walking in the fruits of the Spirit, there's something wrong.

00:04:33.669 --> 00:04:42.291
To walk in the fruits of the Spirit, we have to have the preparation of the gospel of peace on our feet.

00:04:42.291 --> 00:05:03.288
If your shoes are not on your feet—the preparation of the gospel of peace—and you're not walking in peace, you're barefoot and the rest of your armor is messed up because you have to have good shoes on to walk on the serpents and the scorpions with the shield of faith.

00:05:03.288 --> 00:05:10.064
You've got to have all those things to quench all the fiery darts of the wicked.

00:05:15.090 --> 00:05:17.891
You need the sword of the Spirit, which is the word of God, to go and cut that devil up.

00:05:18.275 --> 00:05:24.017
You need to be able to have the helmet of salvation and the breastplate of righteousness.

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:35.100
The spirit of forebodings will come and try to torment you.

00:05:35.100 --> 00:05:47.520
You have got to take authority over that and make sure that whenever you're going into intercession, you're not being tormented by a spirit of forebodings—a fearful apprehension, a feeling that something bad is about to happen.

00:05:47.520 --> 00:05:57.479
You've got to make sure that spirit is not pushing you: 'Something bad's about to happen, we got to intercede.

00:05:57.479 --> 00:06:01.290
' We got to walk that way.

00:06:01.290 --> 00:06:03.780
That's the way it was for me forever.

00:06:13.049 --> 00:06:13.446
I had that for years, always walking around thinking something bad was about to happen.

00:06:13.446 --> 00:06:16.910
'Oh no, I feel heaviness, it must be...

00:06:16.910 --> 00:06:26.237
' And when the Lord showed me this, He said, 'Brandon, this is a spirit of foreboding that's bothering you all the time.

00:06:26.237 --> 00:06:35.437
This isn't a spirit of intercession; you need to be able to learn the discernment of how to divide it.

00:06:35.437 --> 00:06:44.306
' So I started taking authority, and if I start to feel that or anything like that, I go, 'Uh-uh.

00:06:44.306 --> 00:06:51.314
Is this a spirit of forebodings, or is this the Holy Ghost leading me to start interceding for something?

00:06:51.314 --> 00:07:08.820
' When you start binding that spirit back and say, 'No, I will not yield to a spirit of forebodings, but I will yield to the Holy Ghost and I will pray in the Holy Ghost right now,' I bind any spirit; you're not going to torment me because I'm not going to walk in torment.

00:07:08.820 --> 00:07:11.433
Fear hath torment, but perfect love casteth out all fear.

00:07:11.433 --> 00:07:25.245
You can't allow that to happen because I'm telling you, you'll start crawling underneath that rock every day, and it'll keep leading you that way, and you'll live in a heaviness and go around like Eeyore—you know, 'woe is me, everything's falling apart.

00:07:25.245 --> 00:07:26.262
' You can't do that.

00:07:26.262 --> 00:07:31.645
You've got to be the Tigger and go, 'Hey, ha ha, I got joy!

00:07:31.645 --> 00:07:41.537
' I hate to use that as an illustration, y'all, but when you have kids, you see Winnie the Pooh.

00:07:41.537 --> 00:07:51.330
Walk in the spirit of joy, walk in peace, walk in the fruits of the Spirit.

00:07:51.330 --> 00:07:59.019
Another thing I need to tell you: the Holy Spirit is a person.

00:07:59.019 --> 00:08:06.540
He's a gentleman, and when you invite Him into your life, He will...

00:08:06.540 --> 00:08:13.680
last night I was worshiping and He said, 'You've dumped out enough through these videos.

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:16.150
You need to fill yourself back up.

00:08:16.150 --> 00:08:18.282
I need to spend some time with you.

00:08:18.282 --> 00:08:24.165
I need you to separate yourself for a while now.

00:08:24.165 --> 00:08:44.219
' Before all the videos, it has been a big adjustment for me because the time that I'm doing these videos or answering your comments, I used to spend in prayer and worship and seeking Him.

00:08:44.219 --> 00:08:49.230
And He said, 'I need you to just take your time and separate right now.

00:08:49.230 --> 00:08:52.013
Don't make a video; don't think about a video.

00:09:05.274 --> 00:09:05.568
I need you to dip in the river right now.

00:09:05.568 --> 00:09:10.279
I need you to do this for Me.

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:14.974
' And I stopped and I said, 'Well, okay, Lord.

00:09:14.974 --> 00:09:22.833
' And the presence of God took a little bit, and I started getting in there.

00:09:23.380 --> 00:09:24.746
I started singing the song.

00:09:36.934 --> 00:09:37.329
Like I'm telling y'all, I worship Him, and in His presence, there's fullness of joy.

00:09:37.329 --> 00:09:43.050
I said, 'Worship Him,' and I start singing songs and I get into His presence.

00:09:43.050 --> 00:09:52.485
I will enter His gates with thanksgiving in my heart; I enter into those courts, and I will enter in His courts with praise.

00:09:59.049 --> 00:09:59.571
I will say this is the day that the Lord has made.

00:10:06.450 --> 00:10:06.600
I will rejoice and be glad...

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:12.026
He has made me glad, He has made me glad, I will rejoice for He has made me glad.

00:10:12.026 --> 00:10:14.190
You have to get there.

00:10:14.190 --> 00:10:22.440
You have to train yourself to step into that glory river, and the more you do it, the easier and faster you get there.

00:10:22.817 --> 00:10:24.703
It's like a muscle.

00:10:38.370 --> 00:10:38.700
You keep lifting those spiritual weights, you keep working out, and you'll start jumping in those rivers really quick.

00:10:38.700 --> 00:10:48.562
Honestly, when people say, 'Oh, my prayer life is so dry,' you've got to push through those dry times.

00:10:56.914 --> 00:10:57.197
You don't give up.

00:11:01.620 --> 00:11:01.800
You keep pushing through that wall by prayer, thanksgiving, and worship.

00:11:14.571 --> 00:11:14.837
When you get through that wall, you'll get into the river, you'll get in this gusher, and you'll start getting into that flow so strong.

00:11:15.368 --> 00:11:19.079
And that's whenever He'll start taking you places.

00:11:19.079 --> 00:11:21.574
I'll start interceding about things, and I'll hear...

00:11:21.574 --> 00:11:29.640
what's really cool, and I hope this is kind of deep, but you all need a little bit of deep today.

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:32.027
I can hear the prayers of the intercessors outside.

00:11:32.233 --> 00:11:37.365
A lot of times, I'll go into the spirit and I can hear.

00:11:37.365 --> 00:11:52.860
I listen for this one elderly woman—I know she's elderly; I assume she's probably in her 80s because she knows how to flow in the rivers big time—and it's almost like a heartbeat.

00:11:59.700 --> 00:12:06.330
You can start going in the spirit realm like a heartbeat with people in other parts of the world, and you start to sway in, and like a fish, you're swimming in the stream with them.

00:12:06.660 --> 00:12:10.860
You can start swimming in the stream in the spirit with them.

00:12:15.168 --> 00:12:16.205
I notice these intercessors, and the Lord will call me beside them even in my own home.

00:12:16.205 --> 00:12:20.580
I've never met these people, but when I get to heaven, I know I will.

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:33.588
I can go beside them because they always pray at a certain time and I always pray at certain times, and they'll go.

00:12:33.588 --> 00:12:39.051
But inside me, we'll pray and we'll flow in the spirit realm with them.

00:12:44.339 --> 00:12:47.700
I can feel it, and it's like a symphony; it's beautiful music.

00:12:47.700 --> 00:12:54.946
It's a symphony, but we're praying and we're bringing down the strongholds, setting people free and the captives free.

00:13:00.621 --> 00:13:00.866
The spirit realm is more real than the natural.

00:13:04.672 --> 00:13:05.839
I hope you all realize the spirit realm is so real.

00:13:05.839 --> 00:13:19.769
It's so amazing what goes on when you start tapping into the rivers and you start going in with the Holy Ghost and flowing with Him in intercessory prayer.

00:13:19.769 --> 00:13:23.880
You'll start to notice people; you'll start to notice their heartbeat.

00:13:23.880 --> 00:13:28.929
You can feel them in the spirit realm when you're praying.

00:13:28.929 --> 00:13:39.959
I'm not talking about being weird, because some of you get really weird, you know, talking to angels and doing all that stuff.

00:13:39.959 --> 00:13:42.637
I'm not talking about that.

00:13:55.519 --> 00:13:55.746
You pray, and you can get into some really cool stuff in the spirit realm when you're praying and you grow spiritually.

00:14:01.220 --> 00:14:01.479
This is big boy stuff, big girl stuff.

00:14:01.479 --> 00:14:05.340
This isn't little baby stuff I'm talking about; this is deep.

00:14:05.340 --> 00:14:08.914
This is going to the deep rivers.

00:14:08.914 --> 00:14:14.873
I'm trying to tell you all, there's a spirit on this you don't have a clue about.

00:14:16.062 --> 00:14:22.079
A lot of you are clueless about what goes on, even in the cults and the things they do.

00:14:22.079 --> 00:14:28.215
It's time for the body of Christ to grow up and start eating the meat.

00:14:28.215 --> 00:14:34.760
It's time for you to stop drinking the milk; you've been on the milk of the word too long.

00:14:34.760 --> 00:14:45.540
We've got to come up higher; we've got to come up and start grabbing hold of those T-bone steaks—or whatever, you may be vegan and that's your problem.

00:14:45.540 --> 00:14:47.999
Bite some lettuce if you're a vegan, or whatever.

00:14:47.999 --> 00:14:49.320
Let's just flow, y'all.

00:14:49.320 --> 00:14:51.917
Let's not get off on this petty stuff.

00:14:53.886 --> 00:15:01.349
But I'm going to tell you this: we can go into those rivers and, like I said, I could hear the people in Africa praying.

00:15:01.349 --> 00:15:05.579
I can hear the people in Asia praying.

00:15:05.579 --> 00:15:12.548
You can go in and out of those veins and you can pray with them.

00:15:12.951 --> 00:15:16.120
The body of Christ is so cool.

00:15:23.244 --> 00:15:23.436
The spirit realm is so cool, y'all.

00:15:23.436 --> 00:15:27.390
Number two: I was down and really having a hard time.

00:15:31.410 --> 00:15:32.385
I was at my mom and dad's church visiting, and I was worshiping.

00:15:32.385 --> 00:15:38.339
I was dealing with some heaviness—those forebodings I was telling you all about just a little bit ago.

00:15:52.146 --> 00:15:52.404
I was worshiping in their church, and all of a sudden there was a portal that opened up—a massive gateway.

00:16:08.440 --> 00:16:08.847
A portal opened up in the front of the church.

00:16:11.112 --> 00:16:16.440
I could see the ground; it was split where the portal was.

00:16:16.440 --> 00:16:22.740
There was a huge circular portal; it was purple and pink and all kinds of beautiful colors.

00:16:36.298 --> 00:16:36.550
It looked like cotton candy, like a Holy Ghost fog.

00:16:36.803 --> 00:16:37.560
It was beautiful.

00:16:42.240 --> 00:16:42.525
Jesus walks in with these angels—massive warring angels.

00:16:42.525 --> 00:16:47.063
This is the first time I've ever seen Jesus with angels like this.

00:16:54.164 --> 00:16:54.397
He walks in and stands before me.

00:16:54.397 --> 00:17:00.120
Behind where the portal was, it lifted up and I could see all these feet.

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:03.449
They were barefoot; none of them had shoes on.

00:17:03.449 --> 00:17:09.273
I could see gowns and robes, again like what I told you I saw in heaven.

00:17:20.957 --> 00:17:21.223
I asked Jesus, 'What are all the feet?

00:17:21.223 --> 00:17:30.288
' and He said, 'That is part of the great cloud of witnesses, and they've come to watch the service and what's going on here right now.

00:17:30.288 --> 00:17:32.125
' I could hear them all talking.

00:17:34.080 --> 00:17:48.090
You know how when you get in a crowd you can't really understand what they're saying because when you hear a lot of voices together they're saying something—I could hear all the voices talking, but I couldn't make out what they were saying.

00:17:48.090 --> 00:17:50.985
There was activity going on in heaven, but they were watching.

00:17:54.024 --> 00:17:55.512
I could see their gowns and everything behind when Jesus opened up the portal.

00:17:59.753 --> 00:18:09.150
The portal lifted up and I could see in there—some trees and some stuff going on—but all I could see was from their feet to the middle of their waist.

00:18:09.150 --> 00:18:15.739
They were all lined up and looking from heaven into Earth at what was going on in the service.

00:18:19.404 --> 00:18:26.474
The King of Kings visited, and it was amazing; the glory was so thick.

00:18:26.474 --> 00:18:30.773
Jesus came up to me and stood right in front of me.

00:18:32.732 --> 00:18:41.951
It was in the spirit; it wasn't a full manifestation like flesh to flesh, like I had in my kitchen whenever He visited me that time.

00:18:46.320 --> 00:18:46.567
That was too intense; I collapsed.

00:18:46.567 --> 00:18:59.039
But I stood like this in the spirit realm and could see over in the spirit, and Jesus told me, 'My yoke is easy and my burden is light, Brandon.

00:18:59.039 --> 00:19:01.452
You're thinking way too much.

00:19:01.452 --> 00:19:04.200
You're meditating on the wrong thoughts way too much.

00:19:04.200 --> 00:19:09.206
' He said, 'I want you to take the care out of your prayer.

00:19:17.693 --> 00:19:17.980
Be careful for nothing, son; you're full of care.

00:19:17.980 --> 00:19:21.600
' He said, 'Do you see this box?

00:19:21.600 --> 00:19:35.646
' I was inside a big wooden box and I was trying so hard to get out, but I believed I was in this box and that it had a lid on it and I was trapped.

00:19:47.805 --> 00:19:48.150
I was so bound by fear and torment all the time because of things I felt were going on in the world, in my family, and my house—a lot of occultist stuff.

00:19:48.150 --> 00:19:51.432
It was rough at that time.

00:19:51.432 --> 00:19:54.866
Jesus said, 'Brandon, there's no lid on the box.

00:19:54.866 --> 00:19:56.430
You're set free.

00:19:56.430 --> 00:20:02.993
All you've got to do is get out of the box.

00:20:02.993 --> 00:20:06.810
Your thoughts are why you're in the box.

00:20:09.599 --> 00:20:09.959
You're meditating on the wrong things.

00:20:10.942 --> 00:20:13.517
You need to start meditating on the right thing.

00:20:13.517 --> 00:20:17.759
Get in my word and meditate on my word.

00:20:17.759 --> 00:20:22.825
You're meditating too much on the news and these wrong things.

00:20:22.825 --> 00:20:27.000
My yoke is easy and my burden is light.

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:30.750
' He told me, 'You've got to stop thinking so much.

00:20:30.750 --> 00:20:32.909
You think way too much.

00:20:32.909 --> 00:20:35.596
' And He started laughing.

00:20:39.750 --> 00:20:40.133
Jesus started laughing at the circumstances.

00:20:40.133 --> 00:20:43.632
He said, 'Brandon, you've got to start laughing.

00:20:45.255 --> 00:20:46.290
You've got to start enjoying life.

00:20:46.290 --> 00:20:50.482
' He started laughing, and His laugh was so beautiful.

00:20:50.482 --> 00:20:54.180
It was so deep; He chuckled and laughed.

00:20:54.180 --> 00:20:57.087
He had beautiful, white, perfect straight teeth.

00:20:57.087 --> 00:21:02.140
He just laughed and was rejoicing, like, 'You've got to laugh!

00:21:02.140 --> 00:21:05.655
' I was fixed on His face.

00:21:05.655 --> 00:21:08.760
I'd never seen Jesus laugh like this.

00:21:08.760 --> 00:21:21.200
Everything has always been real serious when I've had these visitations, but this time He was laughing and telling me it's time to be full of joy.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.150
He said I had black smudges on my clothes and on me from all of the demonic pressure that I was allowing in my life by my thought life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
I'm not going to tell you anything else He said because it's private, but He was just ministering to me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
He lifted me up and showed me how to get out of that box and get in the word.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
The presence of God was so thick in that service that night.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
The power of God set me free, and I've never been the same since.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
These visitations have changed my life, and I've come to tell you these things because Jesus wants to change your life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
He wants to love on you and tell you how much He loves you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
I just wanted to encourage you all today that His yoke is easy and His burden is light.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
Don't walk in a spirit of heaviness; walk in a garment of praise.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
Be in that place of joy in your life because Jesus loves you so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
There's a great cloud of witnesses watching us, smiling and cheering us on.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
We have such a short amount of time before we get to go home.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Jesus is coming, and I hope this blessed you today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
Father, I thank You that You are bringing a spirit of peace and joy over their lives today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I thank You that there's a garment of praise.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
We give You that praise because You're worthy.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
We give You the honor and glory because You deserve every bit of it, Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
You've cleansed us from all unrighteousness.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
You've taken away all the sin from our lives.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
You took the sickness and disease on your body.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
You took poverty for us, Father.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
I thank you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Mental torment—you took it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
When they put that crown of thorns on your head, you took that on you, Father.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
You said that you took all those things; you became those things so that we don't have to go through them.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
What Jesus bore in his body, I need not bear in mine.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.700
I thank you, Father, that you've set me free by the blood of the lamb and by the word of my testimony.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
My testimony is great: Jesus Christ is my Lord and Savior.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I thank you all for joining me today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
I thank you all for being a part of this little community, my family here.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
I thank you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Please like my videos and share them; it really helps me with the algorithm.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
Jesus loves you so much, and we thank you for being a part of this family.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
